<div id="Idea_3895"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaTitle">
<a href="/akira/dtd/3895-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_3895">Citizen Protection Protocol / Law&nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/8251-4049">vcochran</a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">3 days ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaContent">Require the federal government to create a set of protocols and laws (with penalties) for the protection of US citizens, residents, and visitors whose national and/or cultural origins match those of current or future aggressors upon the US, to be activated in response to foreign aggression.</div>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaFooter"><span style="border-right: 1px solid silver; margin:0 10px 0 0; padding: 0 5px 0 0; color: #666;"><a id="DiscussionTopic_3895" href="javascript:ajaxLink('DiscussionTopicComment_3895', '/akira/discussion.do?mode=comment&dbid=2294&topicID=3895')">Comments (1)</a></span><span id="DiscussionTopicTag_3895"><a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?discussionID=2294">Legal & Policy Challenges</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?mode=tag&tag=human rights">human rights</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?mode=tag&tag=constitutional protections">constitutional protections</a></span></div><div style="margin-top:3px;" id="DiscussionTopicComment_3895"></div>
